  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the response of persistent Barrett's Esophagus and/or dysplasia to focal cyro
      ablation .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Observational study of patients undergoing clinically indicated focal cryo ablation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
